title: NFL Combine Preview, Blake Bortles Extension, Marcus Peters Trade (Football 02/26)
description:
Pete Prisco and Jason La Canfora are set to attend the NFL Combine, but first they have to break down Blake Bortles extension in Jacksonville. Then, the guys preview the week ahead in Indy, and offer analysis on the Marcus Peters trade, and possible Jarvis Landry trade.
